<h1 style="text-align:center;">Empower and Elevate</h1>

<h2>Description</h2>


<p>We are looking to offer mentorships and internships for high school students that are at-risk or of underrepresented backgrounds. Our mentorship program is free of charge for students.</p>
<br>
<p>Empower and Elevate is a non-profit established in 2021</p>
